Raj Rajaratnam’s request for
information from McKinsey & Co. about  Rajat Gupta , a former
senior partner at the consulting firm and former  Goldman Sachs
Group Inc . director, is “critical” to his defense of insider-
trading charges, his lawyer said. Rajaratnam faces trial Feb. 28
in Manhattan federal court.  To contact the reporter on this story:
